Summary:
        * first version enabling dynamic allocation
	* defined CoSupport::SystemC::Event as VPC_Event for internal use
        * added some Controller implementing different scheduling strategies
        * added common interface for preemtable classes -> IPreemptable
        * modified component classes corresponding to IPreemptable
        * removed method minTimeToIdle from all classes implementing it
	* extended p_struct to contain also funcname

	* AbstractComponent:
		- added pointer to listener to enable linear notification within control hierarchy        
		- extended interface for notification mechanism
		- added default implementation for subset of interface
		  declared by IPreemptable
		- changed signature of compute(pcb, funcname) to compute(pcb)

	* ReconfigurableComponent internal changes:
                - fixed destructor
                - changed signature of method setController
                - seperated reconfiguration in loading and storing phase
                - moved loading and storing in case of preemption within
                  schedule_thread

	* Configuration:
		- adjusted interface of configuration to fit to IPreemptable
		- extended properties of configuration with store- and loadtime
		- added priority property 
		- added deadline property

	* AbstractController:
		- removed all basic implementation and added it to new class Controller
		- extended interface with signalPreemption and signalResume

	* AbstractDirector:
		- removed interface compute(name,funcname,event) and compute(name, event), only specific for Director which is used as access to framework
 	
	* VPCBuilder internal changes:
		- added method for controller creation
